<script>
    export default {
      name: "HomePage",
      data: () => ({
        //side bar
        drawer: false,
        group: null,
      }),
      methods: {
        
      }
    }
  </script>
  
  <template>
    <!-- App.vue -->

    <v-app-bar
      color="deep-purple"
      dark
    >
      <v-app-bar-nav-icon @click="drawer = !drawer"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>

      <v-toolbar-title>
        <v-img class="app-title" src="../assets/qwiktime.png"/>
      </v-toolbar-title>
    </v-app-bar>

    <v-navigation-drawer
      v-model="drawer"
      absolute
      temporary
    >

      <v-list
        nav
        dense
      >
        
        <v-list-item-content>
          <v-list-item-title class="text-h6">
            John Leider
          </v-list-item-title>
          <v-list-item-subtitle>john@vuetifyjs.com</v-list-item-subtitle>
        </v-list-item-content>
        <v-system-bar></v-system-bar>
        <v-list-item-group
          v-model="group"
          active-class="deep-purple--text text--accent-4"
        >

          <v-subheader>COMMON</v-subheader>

          <v-list-item class="list-item">
            <v-list-item-icon>
              <v-icon>mdi-home</v-icon>
            </v-list-item-icon>
            <v-list-item-title class="list-text">Home</v-list-item-title>
          </v-list-item>

          <v-subheader>MASTERS</v-subheader>

          <v-list-item class="list-item">
            <v-list-item-icon>
              <v-icon>mdi-account</v-icon>
            </v-list-item-icon>
            <v-list-item-title class="list-text">Customers</v-list-item-title>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list-item-group>
      </v-list>
    </v-navigation-drawer>
  </template>
  
  <style>
    .app-title{
      width: 100px;
    }
  
    .list-item{
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .list-text{
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-left: 20px;
    }
  </style>
